Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the rather "convenient" interaction between Kira and the Japanese police during this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can conclude that Kira and the Japanese police are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Working together"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, Kira is... {\alpha&HFF&}the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that's true, Kira is... the second-generation L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters: {\alpha&HFF&}have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters: have you ever thought, even once, {\alpha&HFF&}that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you at the Japanese Investigative Headquarters: have you ever thought, even once, that your "second-generation" L might be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... I've got no choice now but to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Live on TV, Demegawa is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demegawa, have finally tracked down the base of an evil organization that seeks to capture our God, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And along with my brothers, we have them surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.02,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(365,367)}Transfer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supporters of Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't enter the building all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposition may try and blend in with the crowd and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obey my orders as Kira's spokesman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must corner them, expose them to the cameras, and offer them to Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't overlook you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... {\alpha&HFF&}for now, you'd better get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... for now, you'd better get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a lot of nerve advising me, considering you're Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're still saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are other organizations out there hunting Kira, and yet this attack happens immediately after I start suspecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing is far too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, you're jumping to far too many conclusions from a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To them members present at the Investigative Headquarters, {\alpha&HFF&}at best, Kira is in your midst...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To them members present at the Investigative Headquarters, at best, Kira is in your midst...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}that idea is being reinforced yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is Kira... that idea is being reinforced yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous L also suspected Light-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First squad, break down the door and the first twenty, make your way in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second squad, hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to us! We're the first squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--!! We were here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, unless we get out of here quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What foolish people...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't find it strange that there are people who are willing to support Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that only applies to those that genuinely want Kira to judge criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people besieging this place are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are truly worthless human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're having fun, it's all that matters... they're selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}I realize that, but for now, we need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I realize that, but for now, we need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use L's inheritance and those people we employed that oppose Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But once we use that plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it. The preparations have already been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}M-Money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-{\alpha&HFF&}Money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-Money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's money!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, humans really are amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you can exchange that stuff for apples, so I guess I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! I got that first!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Near, you're planning to escape amid the confusion, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do, Demegawa's cameras should be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pilot! Head toward the floor where the money is coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}Deme-chan, what the hell do you think you're doing?! You can't buy love and peace with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Deme-chan, what the hell do you think you're doing?! You can't buy love and peace with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Lower Manhattan, New York, a vast amount of dollars are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police squads have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police squads?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, given the panic that's ensued here, the police squads have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't looking good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this precise moment, we're safe even if we walk right out the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess in this kind of situation, the police had no choice but to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! So this is how they're intending to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll emerge, disguised as part of the police squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling Aizawa and the others to keep a close eye on the police is as good as telling them that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are police exiting the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to be among them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder just how much money was involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten million dollars maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many apples is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completed installation of communication circuits, so we thought we'd better get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, you're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all at the Investigative Headquarters, {\alpha&HFF&}I believe it won't be long before you each come to a definite decision regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all at the Investigative Headquarters, I believe it won't be long before you each come to a definite decision regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The timing of this attack is as good as saying that Kira is among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if none of you suspect the second-generation L, then you're all worse than nursery school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've reinstated the phone number I gave you all a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to give me a call anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What confidence... {\alpha&HFF&}or rather, he's being pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What confidence... or rather, he's being pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, {\alpha&HFF&}if any of you feel like you want to help Near, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, if any of you feel like you want to help Near, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the current situation, I won't be offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my belief that, ideally, the SPK and ourselves should understand and cooperate with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near's the one that's holding us back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about Deputy Chief Yagami, I don't want to suspect Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. You came home tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Why are you still up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got exams soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Just don't work yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Dad, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be surprising if someone does contact Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is what follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave this even a single step too late, it could turn into an irrecoverable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! An emergency command from Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now... {\alpha&HFF&}number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now... number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Near speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Japanese Investigative Headquarters. I'm Aizawa.
Comment: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally arrived... {\alpha&HFF&}this is so that I'll be completely safe, and a normal wife to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally arrived... this is so that I'll be completely safe, and a normal wife to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Light wants... {\alpha&HFF&}for me to find true happiness in being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Light wants... for me to find true happiness in being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... {\alpha&HFF&}that's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... that's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, L detained two suspects for over 50 days, and the "13 days" rule cleared them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but of course, that on its own doesn't mean that they are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And L had no problems releasing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He had Mr. Yagami, who was Chief at the time, play a trick on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chief informed them that they had been confirmed as Kira and the second Kira, and that they were being taken to an execution chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along the way, the Chief pulled a gun on the suspects and said he'd kill Kira and then himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was believed that if they were Kira, being pushed so far, they would have killed the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the judgment was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's quite a guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira used their detention to prove their innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the suspect offer to be detained?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit, Light-kun did volunteer to be detained...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they did, then this settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who were these two suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite this, I'm still working under L, as a member of the Japanese Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your valuable information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've heard of people with the eyes of a Shinigami being able to see the names of others. That was helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, is that enough? {\alpha&HFF&}You aren't going to question him further?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, is that enough? You aren't going to question him further?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, it's best to leave things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we've learned something vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Chief Yagami and the suspect were father and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other explanation for him saying "I'll kill Kira and then myself".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, {\alpha&HFF&}the second-generation L, and the person I believe to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the second-generation L, {\alpha&HFF&}and the person I believe to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the second-generation L, and the person I believe to be Kira, is... {\alpha&HFF&}Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the second-generation L, and the person I believe to be Kira, is... Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be honest with you... {\alpha&HFF&}I contacted Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be honest with you... I contacted Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. {\alpha&HFF&}It's something that I encouraged myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's something that I encouraged myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I won't ask you that. It might be strange for us to have a discussion about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to establish with absolute certainty that you're not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you have to go through the same thing twice, {\alpha&HFF&}but until Kira's caught, I'd like to keep a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that you have to go through the same thing twice, but until Kira's caught, I'd like to keep a close eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but the same goes for Amane Misa. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll have to check her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but the same goes for Amane Misa. I'll have to check her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always the slight possibility that she has a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Aizawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all become witnesses to the fact that I'm not communicating with Misa in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this cleared up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun not being Kira would be the best outcome, {\alpha&HFF&}but if evidence incriminating him as Kira turns up in Amane's room... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun not being Kira would be the best outcome, but if evidence incriminating him as Kira turns up in Amane's room... {\alpha&HFF&}then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun not being Kira would be the best outcome, but if evidence incriminating him as Kira turns up in Amane's room... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah! Mochii and Monchicchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Light never seems to come home from investigating Kira, I've got nothing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't possibly have the notebook on her in that outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa... there's been a report that a bomb has been planted at L's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most likely a false alarm, but we'd like to check your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Is Light okay?! I better call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is fine. {\alpha&HFF&}He's got some important business to attend to, so he sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is fine. He's got some important business to attend to, so he sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Light loves Misa so much, he'd probably be even more worried if he heard my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search all you want, Aizawa... {\alpha&HFF&}you won't find the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search all you want, Aizawa... you won't find the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it to get awkward around here because of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a friendship club. {\alpha&HFF&}Aizawa and Mogi can do as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a friendship club. Aizawa and Mogi can do as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for Kira's Realm to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.11,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\fscy0\t(0,700,\fscy100)\pos(353,431)\c&H68C3DD&}Kira's Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, supporters of Kira! I am Demegawa, Kira-sama's spokesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold! The construction of Kira's Realm, named after this show, is progressing well thanks to all your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once this is completed, let us all meet here, and welcome Kira-sama to his temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... such bad taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Guess it was a fake report after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as a precaution, one of us better stay here over the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi, you can go back to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Mochii's not staying, but Monchicchi is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dependable enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it... it's just that, without your old hairstyle, you just don't seem like Monchicchi. It's not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to complete Kira's Realm, we beseech you to donate a million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a scam to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're no different from a shady establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.03,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just so unlike Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa... {\alpha&HFF&}he's acting on his own impulses... at this rate, people will start turning away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa... he's acting on his own impulses... {\alpha&HFF&}at this rate, people will start turning away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa... he's acting on his own impulses... at this rate, people will start turning away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need him any longer... {\alpha&HFF&}but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need him any longer... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't find anything in Light-kun and Amane's apartment, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. You can continue observing Misa and me until you're satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I'd like to introduce you to the key members of Kira's Realm, which I myself handpicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will join Kira-sama in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:18:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.78,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,113)\fad(0,500)}Please wait a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}What the hell just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kira after their own followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're stopping someone that's gone too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right, but this is so cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Light-kun nor Amane Misa have had the opportunity to use the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami... {\alpha&HFF&}I can really use him. Selecting him was not a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami... I can really use him. {\alpha&HFF&}Selecting him was not a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami... I can really use him. Selecting him was not a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without orders from me, {\alpha&HFF&}he understands Kira's thoughts, ideals, desires, and what's no longer needed. And he acts upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without orders from me, he understands Kira's thoughts, ideals, desires, and what's no longer needed. {\alpha&HFF&}And he acts upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without orders from me, he understands Kira's thoughts, ideals, desires, and what's no longer needed. And he acts upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had Misa relinquish ownership of her Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had her lose all memories of the Death Note, and send it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can ask her anything, and she won't be able to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is nothing but a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The issue now is the next owner, a man who's already appeared on TV to appeal to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who genuinely worships Kira, a man who understands that just by being given the notebook, he is the chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.02,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(172,56)}Occupation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.02,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(401,54)}Prosecutor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami Teru... {\alpha&HFF&}he is worthy of doing my bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami Teru... he is worthy of doing my bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Shinigami. {\alpha&HFF&}I can now carry out judgments reliably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming, Shinigami. I can now carry out judgments reliably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:51.71,SILLYSIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367,199)\fad(500,500)\fs42\c&H908C8A&\3c&HE0DBDC&}What do you think of Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God.
